									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>210</height>
										<width>145</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>138 folios (+ 2 modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Folios 19-138 (with Hebrew signatures from 8 to 18) form 12 quires of 10 leaves each, with the exception of the quire marked as 12 (folios 69-79), which originally had 12 leaves, one of which has been cancelled.</p>
									<p>One leaf is missing after folio 10, and the last leaf of the quire marked as 18 is also wanting.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Stained.</p>
								</condition>
